Trusted Zone ensured data quality through schema valida￾tion, metadata tracking, and deduplication, integrating video
metadata extraction and JSON normalization alongside struc￾tured data cleaning.

Exploitation Zone transformed cleaned datasets into domain￾specific analytics, including key performance indicators (KPIs),
player performance rankings, and club statistics, powered by PySpark and visualized with Matplotlib.

Consumption Zone provided real-time interaction via the Streamlit-DuckDB dashboard, integrated YOLOv8 video de￾tection for tactical analysis, and conducted sentiment analysis
on YouTube comments using VADER.
